e pleased to offer engaging and transformative experiences that strengthen leadership and social action.  To learn more about membership opportunities and to stay up-to-date on events for prospective and active fraternity and sorority members, please explore the resources housed on our website, in UIC Connection, and via social media!        Important Dates           Get Involved  Connect to student organizations, volunteer, and learn about events!             Join Us  Learn how you can join a Fraternity or Sorority at UIC             Important Dates          All Events                     UIC Logo        Fraternity and Sorority Life          Contact   750 South Halsted Street, 340 SCE, MC 118, Chicago, Illinois 60607-7012  Phone: 312-996-7537  Fax: 312-413-5074  uicgreek@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                 